{
  "stem": "2373.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The beginning was very bad with the hunger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then, you-- you got used to the situation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, you were loosing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was loosing weight all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, so I stayed there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was helping, too, with whatever there was to do to distribute the meal or to help whatever there was needed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was about for two, three weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then Mengele-- that Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mengele-- came in there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, [SPEAKING NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That means qualified nurses, step out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I stepped out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't know it's good or bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I stepped out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was the miracle, what really happened to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because I was taken from-- from there, from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was first sent for-- for disinfection.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was dressed up very nicely.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I got a black winter coat with fur Persian collar.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Only one sleeve was different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I made.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And from there, I went with one of the Aryans-- that is the whoever looked after Gestapo, the German woman-- to Hamburg, Germany in--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Continue?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg your pardon yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went with her from-- directly from Birkenau-Auschwitz to Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On train on [NON-ENGLISH], normally like everybody else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we arrived to Hamburg to a small camp with about 200 people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was one doctor there and one nurse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they needed another nurse, and that was me.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
